FBIS3-55527 "drsov006_b_94005" FBIS-SOV-94-006 Document Type:Daily Report 10 Jan 1994 RUSSIA NATIONAL AFFAIRS Political Issues Commission Discusses Economic Security; Chairman Appointed LD1001152694 Moscow ITAR-TASS in English 1454 GMT 10 Jan 94 LD1001152694 Moscow ITAR-TASS Language: English Article Type:BFN [Text] Moscow January 10 TASS -- The interdepartmental commission of the Russian Security Council on economic security held its first meeting here on Monday. President Boris Yeltsin issued a decree appointing Andrey Zverev, head of the economic division of the Russian Government's office, chairman of the commission. The meeting examined the drafting of a nation-wide economic security doctrine as well as progress in carrying out economic reforms and other issues. The meeting was attended by top executives of ministries and departments represented on the commission.
